body.description: EcoTools Luxe 5-Piece Natural Elegance Makeup Brush Set has luxurious, soft bristles for creating a full-face professional look with an angled liner brush, flat shading brush, tapered blending brush, angled complexion foundation brush, and a soft powder brush. Pair this makeup brush kit with your favorite foundation, concealer, powder, cream, eyeshadow, brow pomade, and gel liner for a complete makeup brush set. These high quality makeup brushes are ecofriendly, vegan, 100% cruelty free, and PETA certified. Pro-Tip spray your makeup brushes with setting spray to increase the pigment or add shimmer. Our makeup brush kit is part of the Luxe collection of sustainable beauty skin care accessories use for making effortless, natural looks with the softest bristles. Clean Beauty. Clean Planet. EcoTools has you covered from head-to-toe to keep you and the planet glowing. From exceptional makeup brushes and blenders to crystal face rollers to a variety of practical bath brushes and accessories, our products are not only effective, but they are also vegan-friendly and cruelty-free. The Delicate Ecopouf made with recycled netting, turns any bath into a spa experience while makeup brush sets like the Start the Day Beautiful Kit help achieve a natural makeup look. EcoTools is the perfect addition to any beauty routine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These brushes are just like the picture. I use them for every day makeup. I am not super experienced with make up, so I did think one of the fluffier brushes would be good for a liquid foundation and then one for a powder, but I don’t think it works as well as a kabuki brush. I do think these are worth the money if you just need some every day brushes and you don’t do super complicated make up!

reviews.reviewText: I bought this set to go with the smaller brush set I had purchased at the same time. The quality is amazing and I have no complaints. They are easy to clean and their integrity doesn't get compromised afterwards. They also retain their shape very well. Would highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 22, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I loved these brushes so much that I bought another set as a back up. I first learned of these brushes from a girl I watch on YouTube... I'm thrilled with them. They are very very very very soft and they perform perfectly. I use them all. My favorite is the eyeshadow and the angled foundation brush. No streaks... No patchiness... No scratchy blending. No wasted product. I've even washed them and they are still perfect. They might be my most favorite brushes that I've ever bought. I know they have a bigger fluffier brush and a small highlighter one in this same brush line and I'm going to buy those too (sold outside of this set)I was NOT paid for my review and I paid my own money for the brushes. My review is real. Just fyi. I have no affiliation with the brand or anyone.

reviews.reviewText: Suaves, no desprenden pelitos y permiten buen difuminado hasta ahora (3 meses de uso).

I bought these for my sister who doesn't use makeup very often but wanted to get more into it. I've been VERY into makeup since I was young and have worked through many, many high-end brushes. These were perfect price-wise for my sister, and the quality was surprisingly high for the price. They are GORGEOUS and girly, which she loved, and have held up well with her beginner practicing.
Son las primeras brochas que compro y las ame, no tiran pelitos y son muy suavecitas.
